Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安咪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是主持人賓碧魯小野木
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是助手岩島京子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  京子  今天的氣氛和以往有些不同哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  今晚的GillNay
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是在浦安市民游泳池的特別攝影場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,節目轉型特別計劃「滿園春色GILLGILL游泳大會」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.07,0:02:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這節目怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法的嘛  這是社長接下工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用穿成這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會嗎  很可愛吶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼不滿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是這意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼來介紹下特邀嘉賓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有田紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  在  我是有田紫苑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也要全力以赴喵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  不行啊  這樣不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,羽澤  你看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:02:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑炭果然可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然啦  她可是我們的秋葉原偶像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和那些雜魚相比等級可不同啊  等級呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙居然看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄得你與我通宵  這真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但必須儘快前去依露瑪說的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.12,0:03:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,報道研的調查還順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,馬馬虎虎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,室戶前輩又那麼靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老闆你的店  還是沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是那麼又髒又亂  儘是些賣不出去的書
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  和學生時代一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  對老闆來說我還只是個孩童啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20\fad(100,300)}（千のプラトー―資本主義と分裂症，\N原書名：MILLE PLATEAUX:(Capitalisme et schizophr'enie)）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是本好書啊  老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an8}（スナックたまき：位於東京都大田區的Snack Bar）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  對不起呀  還在準備呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是來喝酒的  只是想來和你聊一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,齊藤玉城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  庫魯庫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是聯邦搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,關於走私擬態反應芯片  有些事情想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少裝蒜！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做…做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近  你有販賣擬態反應芯片的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算知道  律師不在的場合我什麼都不會說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  我可沒那時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快說！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近賣了6個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,賣給誰了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉  我還有約
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙  來做什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塔斯克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還記得我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你是巴迪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴…巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是說已經很久沒有和你爸爸聯絡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我並不想和現在的老爸見面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你協助了逃犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坦白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經是阿留多人解放戰線「伊茲達魯塔」的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老…老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白說出「伊茲達魯塔」這名字意味著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,標榜著阿留多人解放和主權獲得的恐怖組織
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還引發了中心塔恐怖事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸和那次恐怖爆炸無關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前他已經脫離組織了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塔斯克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的打算退出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你清楚上面都在做些什麼嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們想和克麗絲蒂菈·利比聯手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  這不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個利比大人身為阿留多人卻位居科學所長官之位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即時如此  仍為我們站了出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了  你是個膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是怕死罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能與此扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之後  中心塔就被炸毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那以後的對阿留多人迫害你也清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和老爸勉強得以從奧里奧特拉逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  那傢伙卻又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼  你只要稍微幫點忙就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可是老交情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒絕  我沒打算要幫你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是誤會什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是在求你協助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是在恐嚇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為我會就這麼被抓？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候也會拉你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,順帶還有那個沒用的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  老爸是為了我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴里克和恐怖爆炸也有關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃犯在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是他們的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴里克就藏身在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  說明一下啊  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「伊茲達魯塔」是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上校  是那個搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別出手  畢竟是關照過我們的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我得親自去招待才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還不明白嗎  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪放過我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她是聯邦搜查官  一定會報告的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要趁現在快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  莫斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  聯邦搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和塔斯克接觸過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還蠻喜歡這生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴里克那傢伙  逃跑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有東西貼著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然寫我是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了  老爸  你暫時待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被那孩子抓住也不是件壞事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今還在說這些的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當初就別做什麼亡命專家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  巴迪一定更加難受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會馬上去找新房子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之間你就老實待在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,客人  客房服務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,客房服務？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄錯了吧  我可沒有要過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  為了你預定的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,客房服務哦  塔斯克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來迎接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會耽擱多少時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想問你些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能跟我們走一趟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來沒帶武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿格拉茲涅和迪安謝路兩人被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:14:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遙測器上記錄兩人生命反應消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得是怎麼死的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾  這我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有人盯上我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且好像還知道我們的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你  塔斯克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你背後的是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不會出賣客人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是傳說中的手臂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被稱為「蒼牙」的就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過只是個阿留多人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別大驚小怪  擦傷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過竟然可以傷到我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為阿留多人已經很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼一來  盯著我們的人就消失了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  到此結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴里克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把屍體扔外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「伊茲達魯塔」是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反聯邦政府組織的名稱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中心塔事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和功你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪你有點奇怪啊  自從聽了那些話以後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很正常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯  小那塔魯！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,庫魯庫斯  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是怎麼了  出大事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塔斯克…你爸爸他…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是預感嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有田紫苑？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總算靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸在神田經營這家店也已經有很長一段時間了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我不喝酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛  那喝些飲料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  這個你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,丘樂酷啊  好懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候老爸做給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜歡這個  去那塔魯家裡經常玩的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪你總是馬上就捏壞  讓老爸犯愁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是法羅德先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你是塔斯克的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是兩人份吧  你妹妹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正在睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不說這個  快把這給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都需要一張新面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前問一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殺死老爸的是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殺死塔斯克的是卡特爾他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能以璀璨的聖指起誓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}（聖指：即無名指，是人們使用頻率最低的手指，\N由於不在日常生活中而只在特殊場合體現價值，故有「聖指」一稱）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我以聖指起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  謝謝你告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼也沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  你把硫加解放出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會知道那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是從事研究
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說要使用它的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放…放過我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死在這裡的人也會這麼想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他們連說出這話的時間都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個廢墟正適合作為你們的墓碑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,法羅德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是從第十二個卵中孵化出來的哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？  我睡著了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不過正因如此我才能和老爸單獨對話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會抓住犯人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶是巴迪·希馮·阿魯提拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.40,0:23:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連法羅德都被殺害的逃犯一伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.23,0:23:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來認為犯人是偶了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.34,0:23:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,於是把偶引誘出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後  偶和功遇到了大麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.14,0:23:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奧林  偶會怎麼樣呢
